title: J.D. Vance Gets What He Came For in Ohio, No Elegy Necessary
description: Many Republicans woke up on Wednesday to disappointment. But in Ohio, at least, was the picture of a gambit rewarded as the best-selling author won a Senate seat.
dc:creator: Matt Flegenheimer
media:credit: Maddie McGarvey for The New York Times
media:description: J.D. Vance at his election night party in Columbus after winning the Ohio Senate contest against Tim Ryan on Tuesday.
